 journal; Painesville daily journal. Description based on: Volume I, number 35 (March 9, 1872); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed February 3, 2016). Latest issue consulted: Vol. IX, no. 52, whole no. 468 (June 26, 1880) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed February 3, 2016). Lake County advertiser"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:34.166Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2015270853/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["lake county", "lake", "painesville", "ohio", "united states"], "number": ["936484456", "sn84028196", "online resource", "2470-6620", "2015270853", "sn84028195", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["northern ohio journal (painesville, lake county, ohio) 1872-1896 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 44.74936, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["lake county", "painesville (ohio)", "lake", "painesville", "ohio", "newspapers", "lake county (ohio)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:52:54.074Z", "title": "Northern Ohio journal", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2015270853/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2015270854/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1871", "dates": ["[1871 TO 1872]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with volume I, number I (July 15, 1871); ceased with volume I, number 34 (March 2, 1872). \"A family paper, devoted to literature, science, agriculture and general news.\" Description based on: Volume I, number I (July 15, 1871); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed February 3, 2016). Latest issue consulted: Volume I, number 34 (March 2, 1872) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed February 3, 2016). Northern Ohio journal (